    T - - type of output

    public abstract class PropertyConverter<T>
extends com.bergerkiller.mountiplex.conversion.Converter<java.lang.Object,T>
    Converter to convert to a certain property obtained from various kinds of objects
    These converters are not registered, as they can potentially overwrite data conversions
